Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:14.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you Tsubaki\nthe Dark Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:37.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you came to break the curse,\nit's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:40.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The ceremony is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Troublesome hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:53.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But someone wants to\nborrow your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does a demon want\nwith me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you still bear a grudge\nagainst Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have a clue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't get it at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand a thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:36.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Read the next line, Higurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've forgotten everything\NI learned earlier...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm falling so far behind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome looks so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's that old boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:05.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, the one who jilted Kagome.\NThe jealous, two-timing, bossy guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She probably can't get him\nout of her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just forget him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's not worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:22.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not Inuyasha?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you broke up,\nyou just have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to get over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, well we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:39.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has his kind side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why were you so down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been absent a lot and\nthere's so much schoolwork...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:53.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. You do miss school a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you never miss class,\nit's difficult to follow sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if you keep up and work hard,\nclasses are fun, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Did I say something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so studious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I'm late, he comes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He comes to meet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's {\i1}really{\i0} nice then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nope... He's just jealous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's spoiled!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:35.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Kagome can\nhandle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:46.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What an ominous barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold on tight, old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're here...\NDark Priestess Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:08.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want,\ncalling me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:13.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you remember battling a priestess\nnamed Kikyo fifty years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were trying to steal the\NSacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:20.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... I'm amazed that you know\nof such an old incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dark Priestess Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:26.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you like to use your\nevil powers for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How will helping you\nbenefit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You shall have\nthe Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The old hag\ntransformed herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:03.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:11.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This old woman... sold her soul\nto a demon in order to preserve her youth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, the demon didn't have\nmuch standing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This woman seeks\neven more power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:22.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you really have the Sacred Jewel,\nlet me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:26.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you desire from\nthe Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Eternal youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:37.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku... Just what do you want\nwith me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:43.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one's for Shippo and\nthis is Inuyasha's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't only take sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here... How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still have lots more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:02.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Don't forget the\ncharms and amulets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, are you going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:13.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish I could go back\nin time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you came,\nyou're such a scaredy cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll want to go home\nright away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:27.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's right. Sota, you're\nstill so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you get scared, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:32.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorta used to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you carry it, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:45.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't be helped.\NI'll leave these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome is late!\NShe said she'd be back by dusk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:01.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She said she'd be back by dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:07.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:08.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:15.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sense it, too, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:31.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:40.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sensed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:48.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil is lurking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As though it's crawling\nover the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boy, that was heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!\NW-What's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was bitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:19.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But by what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was bitten... by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:31.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:44.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Paper?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have the girl's blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:08.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:09.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now take me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:13.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So bossy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:30.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was something strange.\NI got it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can handle this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure, as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there's no bite mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There {\i1}was{\i0} something strange there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me see, Inuyasha... That paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way... Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:36.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! This is the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And for you, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How about some of this, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is... Shikigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shikigami?\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:54.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Jewel Shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:12:59.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:00.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miss Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Shards have turned black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:18.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Shards are entering\nmy body...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:26.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Shards which enter the\nwoman's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,synchronize with this Sacred Jewel which\nhas been defiled with Naraku's evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and will slowly fester inside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In both body and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then... her life will be mine\nto control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate this Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:55.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She didn't even realize that\nshe had been cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said she was the reincarnation\nof Kikyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I wondered how formidable she\nwould be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now what shall I do?\NKill her immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us show Inuyasha a\nbad dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:12.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The woman he loves...\nthe woman who wants to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a nostalgic dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagome!\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:19.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede, what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That evil which lurked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone has placed a curse\non Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone's put a curse on her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably the work of\nthe Dark Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome was bitten at the well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:38.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,by the Dark Priestess' messenger\ndemon spirit, {\i1}Shikigami!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dark Priestess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you know of her existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She specializes in curses...\na wicked evil shrine maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's her power that turned the\NJewel Shards black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And they've entered\nher body completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She may die from the poison\nunless we do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll find the Dark Priestess\nand destroy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the only way to\nbreak the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inu... yasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You stay here with Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense evil coming\nfrom this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:30.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get on, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:46.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill who?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:00.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:01.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill who?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:08.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:09.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph! She's resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:24.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is the\nreincarnation of the priestess, Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:26.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She'll require more effort\nthan usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:38.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At that time, Kikyo was infatuated\nwith a half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And her powers were weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:45.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was the perfect opportunity to\nsteal the Sacred Jewel from its guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:01.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She hurled the Shikigami I sent\nstraight back at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relax. I will spare your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That smug look on her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it\nmakes me boil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will she be all right?!\NWill she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will change the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:53.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's hurry, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will Kagome be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:09.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is probably fighting\nthe curse with all her might.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:13.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:15.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The longer it takes, the weaker\nshe'll be to resist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it going to take much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She'll stop resisting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You shall have your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Haven't they found the\NDark Priestess yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can l just watch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Die, Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:36.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get... away, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:49.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:50.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stubborn woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:58.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have control of her body.\NBut her mind still resists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is becoming even more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:05.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:12.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Inuyasha should run out of there,\nthen go ahead and kill Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome is being manipulated\nby the Dark Priestess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, aren't you done yet?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:31.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma is getting stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:07.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can feel it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:25.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This evil... I have faced it once before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:34.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can kill this woman anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:41.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, what will you do?\NBe killed by Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or will you run and\nget Kagome killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get... away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:59.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suffer Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:00.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:51.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before she collapsed, Kagome\nsaid she was bitten by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:54.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was probably the messenger snake\nof the Dark Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:55.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:23:58.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:23:59.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or else, Kagome will\nkill Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:03.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this barrier is too strong...\NI am powerless against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.57,0:24:05.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:06.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:11.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Kikyo and the Dark Priestess!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.74,0:24:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what happened fifty years ago?
